  <summary date="2021-09-13T13:05:58Z" status="Introduced in House">Onward to Opportunity Act

This bill requires the Department of Defense to implement a pilot grant program at five military installations to provide enhanced support and funding to eligible entities to supplement the Transition Assistance Program (TAP) in providing job opportunities for industry-recognized certifications, job placement assistance, and related employment services to service members participating in TAP and their spouses.</summary>
